### Archimedes Python Service API Collection
### Clean, modern Python microservice - Complete API testing suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:8001

###############################################################################
### 🚀 QUICK START WORKFLOW
###############################################################################

# Follow this recommended order for testing:

# 1️⃣ HEALTH CHECK (health.http)
#    └── Verify service is running

# 2️⃣ SCHOOLS (schools.http)
#    └── Create a school first (needed for users)
#    └── Copy the school ID from response

# 3️⃣ AUTHENTICATION (auth.http)
#    └── Register users (use school ID from step 2)
#    └── Login to get access tokens
#    └── Use tokens for protected endpoints

# 4️⃣ TEACHERS (teachers.http)
#    └── Manage teacher records (auto-creates default courses)
#    └── Use school ID from step 2

# 5️⃣ COURSES (courses.http)
#    └── View and manage teacher courses
#    └── Get join codes for student enrollment

# 6️⃣ STUDENTS (students.http)
#    └── Manage student records
#    └── Use school ID and access tokens from previous steps

# 7️⃣ ENROLLMENTS (enrollments.http)
#    └── Student course enrollment
#    └── Join courses with codes or direct enrollment

###############################################################################
### 📁 FILE ORGANIZATION
###############################################################################

# health.http      - System health and documentation endpoints
# schools.http     - School management (create, read, update, delete)
# auth.http        - Authentication (register, login, logout, refresh)
# teachers.http    - Teacher management (CRUD + auto course creation)
# courses.http     - Course management and join code access
# students.http    - Student management (CRUD operations)
# enrollments.http - Course enrollment management

###############################################################################
### 🔧 DEVELOPMENT TOOLS
###############################################################################

# Cleanup Script (when needed):
# python scripts/dev_cleanup.py --force

# Start Server:
# python -m uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8001 --reload

###############################################################################
### 📚 DOCUMENTATION
###############################################################################

# Interactive API Docs: http://localhost:8001/docs
# Alternative Docs:     http://localhost:8001/redoc
# Health Check:         http://localhost:8001/api/v1/health/

###############################################################################
### 🔒 AUTHENTICATION WORKFLOW
###############################################################################

# 1. Create a school (schools.http)
# 2. Register a user with the school ID (auth.http)
# 3. Login to get access_token and refresh_token (auth.http)
# 4. Use access_token in Authorization header for protected endpoints
# 5. Refresh token when needed (auth.http)
# 6. Logout when done (auth.http)

###############################################################################
### 🧪 TESTING NOTES
###############################################################################

# - Replace placeholder UUIDs with actual values from responses
# - Update access_token and refresh_token as needed
# - Use the cleanup script to reset data between test runs
# - Check the FastAPI docs at /docs for schema details